Sentencas: Natural hematite ore is used as a novel electrolyte material for advanced solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Natural Hematite for Next-Generation Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: This hematite-based system exhibits a maximum power density of 225 mW cm(-2) at 600 degrees C and reaches 467 mW cm(-2) when the hematite is mixed with perovskite-structured La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-.
Titulo: Natural Hematite for Next-Generation Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: These results demonstrate that natural materials for next-generation SOFCs can influence the multiutilization of natural resources, thereby affecting the environment and energy sustainability.
Titulo: Natural Hematite for Next-Generation Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
